    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cry of Athena is sandbox battle simulator built for VR and PC where you create epic physics based battles, intervene as a giant god with massive god hands, or join in the battle yourself on the battlegrounds!<strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1174770/extras/9820c39e3befc27598f80a33a4150ae6.webp?t=1728233343\" width=601 height=58 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1174770/extras/a80245507e91975b556a70dd363ccc51.poster.avif?t=1728233343\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1174770/extras/a80245507e91975b556a70dd363ccc51.webm?t=1728233343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1174770/extras/a80245507e91975b556a70dd363ccc51.mp4?t=1728233343\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In Cry of Athena..</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Create your own fully physics based battles with a variety of AI types including the minotaur, siege weapons, and modern day soldiers!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight on the battlefield as a mortal, a god, or simply spectate the battle - the choice is yours!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be a giant god with huge fists that can crush enemies and fling them mercilessly into the skies!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Destroy buildings and deform the voxel based terrain, or build your own levels by shaping the land!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Command your army down to the individual level to follow, charge, or let them act on their own accord!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from a large arsenal of weapons and combat mechanics - fight with sword or bow, guns or cannons, or as a massive all-mighty god.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play in both VR OR non-VR PC!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Local coop in the form of a VR player and a mouse and keyboard player!  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1174770/extras/9820c39e3befc27598f80a33a4150ae6.webp?t=1728233343\" width=601 height=58 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Join the community on our Discord channel in the links to follow development, talk with the developers, keep up with opportunities to participate in testing, and give your own ideas and suggestions!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1174770/extras/2fe6b53d334b0eb30fa81c88c931a704.poster.avif?t=1728233343\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1174770/extras/2fe6b53d334b0eb30fa81c88c931a704.webm?t=1728233343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1174770/extras/2fe6b53d334b0eb30fa81c88c931a704.mp4?t=1728233343\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1174770/extras/9820c39e3befc27598f80a33a4150ae6.webp?t=1728233343\" width=601 height=58 /></span></p>",
